articles.title: Fire involving a car breaks out at Orchard Towers
articles.content: The fire involved a car, said SCDF. Firefighters used a water jet and a fire blanket to extinguish the fire. There were no reported injuries, and the cause of the fire is under investigation. In another video, a fire engine is seen arriving at the scene, which appears hazy with smoke.
